name: nusatrip
tag_list: online-travel, indonesia, airlines, domestic, international, hotels, booking
overview:
1st online travel company in Indonesia to offer domestic & international flights and hotels.

Nusatrip goal is to make travel booking simple in Indonesia. Bringing airlines and hotels into one platform for travelers to chose and compare, combined with a choice of popular local payment methods.

For the 1st time in Indonesia, travelers can search, compare and book airlines from one booking engine. Nusatrip integrate domestic airlines and also international airlines. Finding the right flight or price is now easy.

Nusatrip has also built a large supply (over 100,000 and growing) of hotels in Indonesia, South East Asia and worldwide. All those those hotels are available for booking with instant confirmation 24/7 and can be settle with local payment methods. Again a first in Indonesia. Best of all, the prices are very competitive.
